Read `AGENTS.md` and the relevant files under `.ai/` before making changes.

- Distinguish implemented behavior from planned architecture.
- Preserve tenant isolation and clean architecture dependency direction.
- Do not implement future domains unless explicitly requested.
- Update context docs or ADRs when changing durable boundaries.
- Run `make check` before completing code changes.

